{%- if with_gsd %}
---
version: 1
models:
  research: claude-sonnet-4-6
  planning:
    model: claude-opus-4-6
    fallbacks:
      - openrouter/z-ai/glm-5
      - openrouter/minimax/minimax-m2.5
  execution: claude-sonnet-4-6
  completion: claude-sonnet-4-6
skill_discovery: suggest
auto_supervisor:
  soft_timeout_minutes: 40
  idle_timeout_minutes: 10
  hard_timeout_minutes: 120
budget_ceiling: 100.00
unique_milestone_ids: true
token_profile: balanced
uat_dispatch: true
skill_staleness_days: 60
verification_commands:
  - task lint
  - task test:unit
  - task typecheck
verification_auto_fix: true
verification_max_retries: 2
auto_report: true
git:
  isolation: worktree
  manage_gitignore: false
---

GSD-2 (v2.28+) preferences for {{ project_name }}.
Managed interactively via `/gsd prefs`.

Key settings:
- `models.*` — Per-phase model selection (string or {model, fallbacks} for automatic failover)
- `skill_discovery` — auto / suggest / off
- `auto_supervisor.*` — Timeout thresholds for auto mode
- `budget_ceiling` — USD ceiling; auto mode pauses when reached
- `token_profile` — budget / balanced / quality (coordinated token optimization)
- `unique_milestone_ids` — Unique names to avoid team clashes (e.g. M001-abc123)
- `git.isolation` — worktree (default) or none
- `git.manage_gitignore` — false to skip auto-managing .gitignore
- `skill_staleness_days` — Skills unused for N days get deprioritized (0 = disabled)
- `verification_commands` — Commands run after each task to verify correctness
- `verification_auto_fix` — Auto-fix lint/format issues on verification failure
- `verification_max_retries` — Max retries before escalating verification failure
- `auto_report` — Generate HTML reports after milestones (`/gsd export --html --all`)

Docs: https://github.com/gsd-build/GSD-2/blob/main/docs/configuration.md
{%- endif %}
